The <em>vitacontrol </em>cooking assistant which can be operated intuitively is an integral part of the vitavit edition and is available as an accessory for the <em>vitavit premium</em> line. It can be attached to the valve with a single click.&nbsp;
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div>With optical and acoustic signals it helps set the ideal cooking temperature and time. The cooking assistant can be used on various stove types and can also remind you to replace seals and the battery. <em>vitacontrol </em>can also be used as an autonomous short-cycle timer.</div>
